headline.main: No. 15 Florida State Earns Second Seed in ACC Tournament
headline.print_headline: No. 15 Florida State Earns Second Seed in ACC Tournament

lead_paragraph: Florida State's 66-57 victory over No. 25 Miami on Saturday gives the 15th-ranked Seminoles a double-bye in the Atlantic Coast Conference Tournament and their first unbeaten home season in 41 years.
